

| Pattern              | Purpose                                                                         |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Singleton**        | Ensures a class has only one instance and provides a global point of access.    |
| **Factory Method**   | Delegates the object instantiation to subclasses.                               |
| **Abstract Factory** | Produces families of related objects without specifying their concrete classes. |
| **Builder**          | Separates object construction from representation.                              |
| **Prototype**        | Clones existing objects without depending on their classes.                     |
